body: '4.0 out of 5 stars''Small and medium trolley was good for the price with dual wheels packing could have been made in carton box it was only covered by polythene cover which makes small scratches. Worth for the price'

title: 'Bag is as shown'
body: 'The bag is delivered nicely as expected. No scratch or anything broken. The quality is not too good but you get what you pay for. Handles zipper wheels are adequately nice'

title: 'Good product for carrying during travel.'
body: 'Very useful product for travelling  Very light and empty space with solid state and good zipper with secure locking pin.'

title: 'कृपया ग्राहक आपके पास आकर जो समान लेना चाहता है उसे जांच परख कर भेजा करिये धन्यवाद'

title: 'Good Quality For International Flight'
body: 'Its well portable of 55cm trolleys. Thickness good also Design Appearance is good fibre is hard and durable. I recieved it with no damage.  Overall nice product !'

title: 'Bad Experience.'
body: 'number lock is not working poor quality.The company is unable to guarantee product quality.'

title: 'Very bad quality product'
body: 'Very bad quality product. Cheap quality material. Scratches comes very often. Color also looked dull. Wheels also very bad quality.'

title: 'Cabin luggage'
body: 'Good finishing with adequate space but one out side compartment is required for carrying gadgets'

title: 'Awesome product'
body: 'Product was awesome. It is worth for money.quality was very good'

title: 'did not met my expectations'
body: 'did not deliver on give time as well as delivery date extended without prior notice. So the booking was cancelled.'

title: 'Good Product'
body: 'The media could not be loaded. Product good quality as per price level .'

title: 'Handle frame is inside the bag'
body: 'Handle frame is inside the bag which is not a major issue but in case you want to put something rigid indise the bag you may lose a couple of inches in space'

title: 'Small suitcase'
body: I ordered this product for my travelling purpose but it is very small. It's similar to cabin size bag. Quality is good. Worth it for money. I purchase new one because of its small size.

title: 'Very good product.'
body: 'Very good product with rigid build quality. Value for money.'

title: 'Review about and Quantity and Quality'
body: 'Recently bought this trolley with combo of two different sizes. 1.Quality wise also its good.  2.Quanity- Small one is good for 3days travel. And the medium size i have added an image i can able to keep 2layers of Roll. when I roll my shirts and t-shirts in single side with that i can able to keep around 28 shirts or t-shirts comfortably  The quality i have filled is 28 t-shirts  2Mini towel  5pairs of socks in single side.  Worth to buy'

title: 'Good'
body: 'But the middle handle is not suitcase that only problem other wise product is good'

title: 'Value for money'
body: 'Good quality for the price. Wheels are the best. Inner quality is good. Comfortable for a 3 or 4 days trip.'
